    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute gem! It is in stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s pristine inside and out without a single scratch to worry about. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this beauty is waiting for you. Come take it for a spin and fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
