      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s specimen, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior finish is flawless, retaining its deep factory luster with no swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, thanks to climate-controlled garage storage and a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dash is free of UV damage, and it still carries that new-car scent. Every electronic component and mechanical system operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Accompanied by a meticulous binder of all service records, both original keys, and the factory window sticker, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It has been driven sparingly and maintained with an open checkbook, making it an ideal acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
